    <chapter>
      <heading>
        Software documentation for the MPGONMR2DSpectrum class
      </heading>
      <class name="MPGONMR2DSpectrum" super="MPGOSpectrum">
        <declared>MPGONMR2DSpectrum.h</declared>
        <desc>
          2-D NMR spectrum (e.g. HSQC, COSY): a row-major float64
          intensity matrix of `width × height` points plus F1
          and F2 axis descriptors. The matrix is stored on disk as
          a flattened 1-D dataset with the shape recorded in scalar
          attributes; this is sufficient for round-trip
          fidelity and keeps the HDF5 wrapper API surface
          small. A future milestone may switch to a native 2-D
          dataset.
        </desc>
